Stephen A. Kubiatowski, Senior Vice President and Deputy General Counsel of Kindred Healthcare, has been nominated to serve as a Judge on the United States Court of Federal Claims. He has extensive experience in litigation, investigation, and regulatory matters. Kubiatowski previously worked as a Partner at Faegre Baker Daniels LLP and has dedicated 20 years to public service, including positions at the United States Department of Justice and as an Assistant United States Attorney. He clerked for Judge Michael Kanne of the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit. Kubiatowski holds a B.A. from Dartmouth University and a J.D. from Columbia University School of Law, where he was the Managing Editor of the Journal of Transnational Law.